steps.command: $NameSpace = Get-WmiObject -Namespace "root" -Class "__Namespace" | Select Name | Out-String -Stream | Select-String "SecurityCenter";$SecurityCenter = $NameSpace | Select-Object -First 1;Get-WmiObject -Namespace "root\$SecurityCenter" -Class AntiVirusProduct | Select DisplayName, InstanceGuid, PathToSignedProductExe, PathToSignedReportingExe, ProductState, Timestamp | Format-List;
steps.plaintext_command: $NameSpace = Get-WmiObject -Namespace "root" -Class "__Namespace" | Select Name | Out-String -Stream | Select-String "SecurityCenter";$SecurityCenter = $NameSpace | Select-Object -First 1;Get-WmiObject -Namespace "root\$SecurityCenter" -Class AntiVirusProduct | Select DisplayName, InstanceGuid, PathToSignedProductExe, PathToSignedReportingExe, ProductState, Timestamp | Format-List;
